ROLEPLAYING GUIDELINES

AetherMUD is a roleplaying game first.

  - Stay in character in the game world. Use say, emote, and whisper in rooms.
  - Use OOC for out-of-character questions and staff contact.
  - Use introduce before expecting others to know your character's name.
  - Use telepathy or radio for remote contact as appropriate.

Power gaming, killing new characters without story reason, and ignoring
scene context reduce fun for everyone.

SEE ALSO: introduce, consent, communication, ooc
